_sText:
Finally I've gotten time to finish Sluice. Most people have probably played the beta, since it's been in rotation on the ksf timer-server for a while, but that was not a finished map..

*Fixes*
Fixed the Fps-issues that occured midway through the map.
Hundreds of texture corrections.
Optimization throughout the entire linear part.
Probably more, can't remember.

*Additions since the beta*
Added a 5-staged map as a bonus.
Several new easter-eggs, which are spread out through the map. The entrance to the "bonus-map" is hidden, and you have to find it yourself. (Although most of you will just noclip :c)
****
I hope everyone will enjoy the map, and I'd like to thank Sangre and Billy for their amazing contributions, which makes me look an awful lot like a rookie when it comes to map-design.. ;)

Also, I'd like to thank Ryan S and Power-Fusion, because the jails they started for this map were freaking awesome, it's just a shame that they never got finished in time. Can't wait much longer because I'm going to the army etc, so the map is getting released as-is.

~razer.
